	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />OK, answering your question, most emulators don't emulate the GG patching hardware, so even a patched NES ROM would ignore your code. Adding GG support to an emulator would be pretty easy, though.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


