	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>Re: help needed for game genie with emulators question.</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Nintendulator doesn't support NTSC encoding and decoding; Nestopia does. And I haven't checked how much CPU is needed for puNES; Nestopia ran on an old 866 MHz P3, and even on newer machines other than Atom, less CPU use means less heat.<br /><br />(Side note: blargg, where's your NTSC library hosted now?)

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


